Z(T):= \sum_{n=1}^\infty \exp \left(\frac{-E(n)}{k_B T}\right) = \sum_{n=1}^\infty \exp \left(\frac{-E_0 \log n}{k_B T}\right) \equiv \sum_{n=1}^\infty \exp \left(-s \log n\right) = \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{n^s} = \zeta (s)
